tspan.tspan: In this task, you need a mouse and earphones/speakers.
You will see 9 purple blocks and a "Done" button.
Several of the blocks will "light" up in a specific order.
Once you hear the word "go", you need to click the
highlighted blocks in the same order and then click
It starts easy and becomes gradually more difficult. Try to
get as far as you can.
Press the space bar when ready to start
